* For the sake of others reading your code and either helping you or grading you, don&#39;t be afraid to use whitespace to make your code more readable. Page real estate is not that expensive. Also read up on and use Java naming conventions including capitalizing the first letter of class names.  This will make it much easier for others (us!) to read and understand your code.

